## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **dantrolene Dantrium / Ryanodex 2014 reformulation** = 악성 고열증 1L + heat stroke off-label rescue. RyR1 ryanodine receptor block — Ca leak suppression. quantum-VQE 의 RyR1 pocket 가 직접 fit. heat stroke 임상 RCT 부재 — observational benefit only.
2. **acetazolamide Diamox 1953** = AMS 예방 + 경증 치료 1L. carboxylic anhydrase — metabolic acidosis 유도하여 ventilatory drive 자극. cross-glaucoma 와 mechanism 동일. quantum-VQE pocket fit.
3. **nifedipine + sildenafil/tadalafil HAPE** = pulmonary vascular tone 감소. PAH (cross-pulmonology) 와 mechanism overlap. evidence quality moderate (small RCT).
4. **dexamethasone HACE/AMS 중증** = brain edema 감소. classical 응급 — mechanism vs underlying hypoxia 가 직접 X. observational benefit dominant.
5. **portable hyperbaric Gamow bag** = O2 supplemental 부재 시 altitude descent 시뮬레이션. evacuation 까지 bridge therapy. WEAVE fabric scaffold 가 직접 fit.
6. **tafenoquine Krintafel/Arakoda 2018** = first-in-class 8-aminoquinoline single-dose radical cure P. vivax/ovale. G6PD 유전형 검사 필요. climate malaria expansion 으로 적응증 확대 (cross-tropical_ntd).
7. **dengue Qdenga 2022** = 4-serotype live-attenuated tetravalent. Dengvaxia 2019 의 seronegative 위험 회피. climate dengue expansion 으로 vaccinology 우선순위 상승 (cross-vaccinology).
8. **PM2.5 + ozone-related asthma ICS step-up** = budesonide-formoterol / fluticasone-salmeterol classical. climate-driven 만성 노출 = step-up 빈도 증가. evidence epidemiologic dominant.
9. **eco-anxiety + climate grief SSRI** = sertraline/escitalopram repurpose. evidence weak — formal RCT 부재. clinical practice 가 generalized anxiety/MDD framework 적용.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, climate-health 임상 의미 한정. heat stroke + AMS 표준 치료 임상 evidence 의 대부분 small RCT + observational.

